                    <span>As someone who has quite a bit of experience with animation programs, but little exposure to Flash, I found this book to be very useful.  It's written in a lively, entertaining manner and Mark Clarkson manages to describe difficult procedures in terms even those new to Flash can understand.</span>
                  
              
